---
title: Steak Fajitas with Kiwi Salsa, Roasted Veggies and DIY Refried Beans
description: The colour gold signifies riches, glitz, and extravagance—all apt adjectives to describe this dish. Its centerpiece is a salsa based around kiwis, which have sweet flesh in that opulent hue. But there are also some equally luxe accompaniments, like deeply spiced strips of beef and a nice dab of sour cream.
